Architecture Flow

1. Users interact with the frontend interface.


2. React components send requests to backend APIs.


3. The Node.js and Express server processes requests.


4. MongoDB stores and retrieves user data.


5. The Adaptive Learning Engine analyzes study behavior.


6. Personalized recommendations and analytics are returned to the user dashboard.



